commit.message: Add option to use formal grammar.
Parse files with standard Python grammar.
Use our copy of the grammar.
Add cdef function declarations to the grammar.
Add typed and optional arguments to the grammar.
Add type qualifiers to the grammar.

Add C int types to the grammar.

This is admittedly a bit ugly, but very widely used.
Allow cname specifications in the grammar.
Add visibility, extern gil_spec to grammar.
Add variable declaration assignment to the grammar.

Allow Cython keywords to be used as names.

Only cdef, cpdef, and ctypedef are dissallowed.
Add visibility, cdef decorators to grammar.
Add IF and DEF to grammar.

Merge branch 'grammar3' into grammar-merge

Conflicts:
	Cython/Parser/Grammar
Add 'not None' and nested template types to grammar.
Add sed script to move declarators to types.
Update header of Cython grammar file.
